      ==
  %=  this
    settings  :*
                [.500 .500] 
                *radius
                *address
                *(map id collection)
                *banned
                %anyone
              ==
  ==
:: 
++  on-save  !>(state)
::
++  on-load  
  |=  old-vase=vase
  ^-  (quip card _this)
